1
00:01:01,960 --> 00:01:03,640
The fish soup is here.

2
00:01:04,680 --> 00:01:05,840
Sorry for the wait.

3
00:01:05,840 --> 00:01:07,100
Here is your fish soup.

4
00:01:07,480 --> 00:01:08,800
Let me serve you a bowl.

5
00:01:09,760 --> 00:01:11,020
We'll do it ourselves.

6
00:01:13,160 --> 00:01:14,090
Enjoy your meal.

7
00:01:44,400 --> 00:01:45,440
How attentive.

8
00:01:46,640 --> 00:01:47,800
Such a temper.

9
00:01:47,800 --> 00:01:49,060
Are you still mad at me?

10
00:01:54,640 --> 00:01:56,100
The fish soup is poisoned.

11
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:04,680
Could it be Mother's men?

12
00:02:07,520 --> 00:02:08,960
It seems when we left the city gates,

13
00:02:08,960 --> 00:02:10,360
we were still suspected.

14
00:02:10,639 --> 00:02:11,700
The waiter is gone.

15
00:02:11,760 --> 00:02:12,960
He's not from the inn.

16
00:02:14,920 --> 00:02:16,650
Let's go back to the room first.

17
00:02:36,520 --> 00:02:38,250
Since you've already found out

18
00:02:38,520 --> 00:02:40,320
that the fish soup wasn't poisoned,

19
00:02:40,320 --> 00:02:42,180
and only Her Ladyship's bowl was,

20
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:44,400
then the poisoner...

21
00:02:44,400 --> 00:02:45,400
can only be you.

22
00:02:45,760 --> 00:02:47,420
If I really wanted to kill her,

23
00:02:47,560 --> 00:02:49,560
why would I save her from danger so many times?

24
00:02:49,560 --> 00:02:52,960
Of course, it's for the ledger of the gold embezzlement case.

25
00:02:55,480 --> 00:02:57,920
You failed to steal the ledger in the palace,

26
00:02:57,920 --> 00:02:59,360
so you changed your identity,

27
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:00,080
followed us all the way,

28
00:03:00,080 --> 00:03:01,810
and waited for an opportunity.

29
00:03:01,840 --> 00:03:02,920
I just don't know

30
00:03:03,160 --> 00:03:04,820
if you are General Shen's man,

31
00:03:05,760 --> 00:03:07,890
or if there's someone else behind you.

32
00:03:09,160 --> 00:03:10,240
Tell me.

33
00:03:10,240 --> 00:03:11,170
What's going on?

34
00:03:12,960 --> 00:03:13,760
Not again.

35
00:03:14,280 --> 00:03:16,920
It was indeed me who stole the ledger in the palace,

36
00:03:16,920 --> 00:03:18,720
but he was wrong about one thing.

37
00:03:19,160 --> 00:03:20,560
I am indeed your cousin.

38
00:03:21,600 --> 00:03:22,760
Otherwise,

39
00:03:22,760 --> 00:03:25,079
with General Shen's wise and suspicious nature,

40
00:03:25,079 --> 00:03:26,680
why would he trust me so much?

41
00:03:26,760 --> 00:03:28,200
I just don't understand

42
00:03:28,880 --> 00:03:31,160
why she would attack you.

43
00:03:31,200 --> 00:03:32,000
Mr. Zhao,

44
00:03:32,640 --> 00:03:34,170
don't dodge the main issue.

45
00:03:34,640 --> 00:03:36,100
Who do you really work for?

46
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:40,860
Are you interrogating me?

47
00:03:43,000 --> 00:03:45,730
Since Mr. Zhao wants to travel with Her Highness,

48
00:03:47,040 --> 00:03:49,640
you should naturally treat us with sincerity.

49
00:03:51,600 --> 00:03:53,860
I have no hidden agenda in following you.

50
00:03:53,920 --> 00:03:56,180
My only purpose is to ensure your safety.

51
00:03:56,600 --> 00:03:57,600
Although

52
00:03:57,600 --> 00:03:59,200
I work for General Shen,

53
00:04:00,080 --> 00:04:01,610
I don't want you to get hurt.

54
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:03,740
Even if you won't take my life,

55
00:04:04,880 --> 00:04:05,840
dare you say

56
00:04:06,440 --> 00:04:08,040
you haven't deceived me at all

57
00:04:08,040 --> 00:04:09,700
and have no ulterior motives?

58
00:04:11,120 --> 00:04:12,580
What motives could I have?

59
00:04:13,360 --> 00:04:14,800
I saved your lives.

60
00:04:14,800 --> 00:04:16,440
I paid for your expenses.

61
00:04:16,440 --> 00:04:17,899
And I did all the fighting.

62
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:22,680
If I really have an ulterior motive,

63
00:04:25,560 --> 00:04:26,600
I would hope

64
00:04:27,280 --> 00:04:29,340
you could fall in love with me one day.

65
00:04:30,040 --> 00:04:31,570
Does that count as a motive?

66
00:04:42,280 --> 00:04:43,280
You

67
00:04:43,440 --> 00:04:44,900
shouldn't have saved her.

68
00:04:45,080 --> 00:04:46,680
She is an ungrateful wretch.

69
00:04:47,280 --> 00:04:49,520
She was just betrayed by her closest kin.

70
00:04:49,520 --> 00:04:51,840
It is right for her not to trust anyone.

71
00:04:52,920 --> 00:04:53,880
Yeah.

72
00:04:54,400 --> 00:04:56,280
You are so great.

73
00:04:56,520 --> 00:04:59,380
Not only do you save the sweetheart who stabbed you,

74
00:04:59,520 --> 00:05:02,200
but you also have to save your sweetheart's sweetheart.

75
00:05:02,200 --> 00:05:03,200
Shut your mouth.

76
00:05:23,080 --> 00:05:25,210
You like looking at me so much, cousin?

77
00:05:25,680 --> 00:05:26,480
Robbery!

78
00:05:29,280 --> 00:05:30,160
Robbery!

79
00:05:32,360 --> 00:05:34,200
Stop! Robbery!

80
00:05:34,560 --> 00:05:35,520
Put down your weapons

81
00:05:35,520 --> 00:05:36,480
and surrender!

82
00:05:36,840 --> 00:05:37,560
I advise you all

83
00:05:37,560 --> 00:05:38,560
to behave.

84
00:05:38,560 --> 00:05:40,600
Do you see my armor?

85
00:05:41,200 --> 00:05:43,840
I belong to the Northern Army.

86
00:05:43,840 --> 00:05:44,920
If you dare to make a move,

87
00:05:44,920 --> 00:05:46,050
we will kill you all.

88
00:05:46,440 --> 00:05:47,500
The Northern Army.

89
00:05:48,280 --> 00:05:49,540
Baili Jinghong's men.

90
00:05:57,280 --> 00:05:58,720
I wonder which general

91
00:05:58,920 --> 00:06:00,560
you serve under

92
00:06:00,560 --> 00:06:02,160
in the Northern Border Army.

93
00:06:02,720 --> 00:06:04,720
You wouldn't know even if I told you.

94
00:06:04,840 --> 00:06:06,200
The Jade-Faced Fierce General,

95
00:06:06,200 --> 00:06:07,880
Young General Jiuying.

96
00:06:07,880 --> 00:06:09,080
Have you heard of him?

97
00:06:18,040 --> 00:06:20,440
Top-grade cloud brocade. You must be rich.

98
00:06:21,320 --> 00:06:22,240
I advise you

99
00:06:22,240 --> 00:06:24,480
to hand over all your silver immediately.

100
00:06:24,480 --> 00:06:26,240
Otherwise... Humph.

101
00:06:37,120 --> 00:06:38,720
What did the Second Boss eat?

102
00:06:38,760 --> 00:06:40,159
The smell is too pungent.

103
00:06:42,560 --> 00:06:44,200
Take them away.

104
00:06:59,480 --> 00:07:00,760
The Second Boss is back.

105
00:07:00,760 --> 00:07:02,480
The Second Boss is back.

106
00:07:03,040 --> 00:07:04,280
Hurry, keep up.

107
00:07:04,280 --> 00:07:05,240
Behave.

108
00:07:05,240 --> 00:07:06,560
You rich people,

109
00:07:06,920 --> 00:07:08,880
let's see how I deal with you.

110
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:10,800
Brother.

111
00:07:11,120 --> 00:07:12,160
Second Brother.

112
00:07:12,160 --> 00:07:13,020
Little sister.

113
00:07:14,360 --> 00:07:15,320
Look, Boss.

114
00:07:15,800 --> 00:07:16,920
I brought them back for you.

115
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:18,440
This batch is all rich people.

116
00:07:18,440 --> 00:07:19,560
Brothers, uh,

117
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:21,090
take off their blindfolds.

118
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:23,860
Okay, let's see how these fat sheep look.

119
00:07:28,640 --> 00:07:29,640
Boss, take a look.

120
00:07:31,880 --> 00:07:32,720
How are they, Boss?

121
00:07:32,720 --> 00:07:33,680
Not bad, right?

122
00:07:35,520 --> 00:07:37,120
Yeah, this batch is not bad.

123
00:07:37,120 --> 00:07:38,080
Take them inside.

124
00:07:38,080 --> 00:07:38,840
Go.

125
00:07:39,360 --> 00:07:40,600
Take them all.

126
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:41,760
Go.

127
00:07:44,720 --> 00:07:45,480
Hehe.

128
00:07:45,720 --> 00:07:46,760
Let me tell you, little sister.

129
00:07:46,760 --> 00:07:48,360
As soon as I showed up,

130
00:07:48,360 --> 00:07:49,320
the armor on my body,

131
00:07:49,320 --> 00:07:50,920
they had never seen it before.

132
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:51,640
Really?

133
00:07:53,200 --> 00:07:55,240
I was so majestic.

134
00:07:56,280 --> 00:07:58,480
These weaklings from the city

135
00:07:58,480 --> 00:08:01,280
were almost paralyzed on the spot.

136
00:08:01,600 --> 00:08:02,840
You're really amazing, Second Brother.

137
00:08:02,840 --> 00:08:03,800
Let me tell you.

138
00:08:03,800 --> 00:08:05,930
These rich people have no experience.

139
00:08:06,280 --> 00:08:07,320
They only have money.

140
00:08:07,320 --> 00:08:08,920
We'll torture them well later. Mother.

141
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:10,200
Who are they?

142
00:08:10,200 --> 00:08:12,720
Did the Boss rescue them too?

143
00:08:12,960 --> 00:08:14,600
Why are they tied up?

144
00:08:15,800 --> 00:08:17,760
Those brought back tied up are definitely not good people.

145
00:08:17,760 --> 00:08:18,820
Don't look at them.

146
00:08:19,120 --> 00:08:22,920
Careful, you might get beaten to death by them like your big brother.

147
00:08:24,880 --> 00:08:25,880
Hurry inside.

148
00:08:26,120 --> 00:08:26,600
Hurry.

149
00:08:27,640 --> 00:08:28,280
Get in.

150
00:08:28,320 --> 00:08:29,120
Hurry up.

151
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:45,620
Where is your general?

152
00:08:46,600 --> 00:08:47,880
Behave and write a letter first.

153
00:08:47,880 --> 00:08:49,360
Have someone come to ransom you.

154
00:08:49,360 --> 00:08:50,760
If no one ransoms you,

155
00:08:50,880 --> 00:08:52,720
we'll skin you alive.

156
00:08:55,320 --> 00:08:59,000
I didn't expect the Northern Border Army to have such terrifying methods.

157
00:08:59,000 --> 00:09:00,840
I haven't heard of this before.

158
00:09:01,840 --> 00:09:02,640
Hmph.

159
00:09:03,400 --> 00:09:04,840
Have some water first.

160
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:06,440
Oh, sister.

161
00:09:06,800 --> 00:09:07,800
They haven't even paid yet.

162
00:09:07,800 --> 00:09:09,730
Why are you being so polite to them?

163
00:09:22,480 --> 00:09:23,640
Second Boss.

164
00:09:23,640 --> 00:09:26,160
Please save my husband.

165
00:09:26,320 --> 00:09:27,440
Dr. Zheng said

166
00:09:27,640 --> 00:09:29,720
if we don't get money to buy medicine down the mountain,

167
00:09:29,720 --> 00:09:31,760
he won't survive for three days.

168
00:09:31,760 --> 00:09:33,120
Second Boss,

169
00:09:33,120 --> 00:09:34,760
Miss Doukou,

170
00:09:35,120 --> 00:09:37,440
please give me ten more copper coins to save his life.

171
00:09:37,440 --> 00:09:38,800
Get up.

172
00:09:39,160 --> 00:09:40,040
I beg you.

173
00:09:40,040 --> 00:09:41,320
Hurry, get up.

174
00:09:43,080 --> 00:09:44,800
My Huzi is still young.

175
00:09:44,800 --> 00:09:46,360
He can't live without a father.

176
00:09:46,360 --> 00:09:50,040
I kowtow to you. I beg you.

177
00:09:50,040 --> 00:09:52,200
Please.

178
00:09:53,080 --> 00:09:55,320
In pursuit of longevity,

179
00:09:55,320 --> 00:09:58,080
the late emperor spent thousands of taels of silver just to eat a fish.

180
00:09:58,080 --> 00:10:02,140
Escorting it all the way sacrificed many elite soldiers and fine horses.

181
00:10:02,440 --> 00:10:03,600
What a sorrowful world.

182
00:10:03,600 --> 00:10:05,840
I beg you, Second Boss.

183
00:10:06,360 --> 00:10:07,680
Come.

184
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:09,800
Here, this is for you.

185
00:10:10,320 --> 00:10:11,880
Get up.

186
00:10:13,400 --> 00:10:14,720
It's not enough.

187
00:10:14,720 --> 00:10:16,960
Well, I don't have any more either.

188
00:10:23,800 --> 00:10:25,000
Thank you, Second Boss.

189
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:27,680
Thank you, Miss Doukou.

190
00:10:27,880 --> 00:10:28,880
Go.

191
00:10:34,040 --> 00:10:35,240
Hero,

192
00:10:35,240 --> 00:10:37,360
aren't you under General Jiuying's command?

193
00:10:37,360 --> 00:10:38,840
So shabby.

194
00:10:39,360 --> 00:10:40,960
Giving so little money,

195
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:42,720
it's not even enough for a dose of medicine.

196
00:10:42,720 --> 00:10:43,980
None of your business.

197
00:10:44,160 --> 00:10:45,040
Mind your own business.

198
00:10:45,040 --> 00:10:47,520
If no one comes to ransom you,

199
00:10:47,840 --> 00:10:49,400
I will slaughter you all.

200
00:10:50,280 --> 00:10:51,720
Do I still need to be ransomed?

201
00:10:51,720 --> 00:10:53,720
I can give you gold right now.

202
00:10:54,040 --> 00:10:54,960
What?

203
00:10:55,960 --> 00:10:57,280
You have gold on you?

204
00:11:00,080 --> 00:11:01,810
I don't have any on me right now.

205
00:11:01,920 --> 00:11:02,680
But,

206
00:11:03,160 --> 00:11:06,040
this mountain of yours actually has a

207
00:11:06,760 --> 00:11:07,600
gold mine.

208
00:11:07,640 --> 00:11:08,640
What?

209
00:11:08,640 --> 00:11:10,040
A gold mine?

210
00:11:11,560 --> 00:11:12,720
Hey, boss.

211
00:11:13,320 --> 00:11:16,320
This kid says there's a gold mine on our mountain.

212
00:11:16,400 --> 00:11:18,440
He's glib and looks like a gigolo.

213
00:11:18,440 --> 00:11:19,400
Can we trust his words?

214
00:11:19,400 --> 00:11:21,400
In our rundown Beimang Mountain,

215
00:11:21,400 --> 00:11:23,260
could there really be a gold mine?

216
00:11:23,320 --> 00:11:24,680
Don't you have the manpower?

217
00:11:24,680 --> 00:11:25,840
You might as well give it a try.

218
00:11:25,840 --> 00:11:27,080
Easy for you to say.

219
00:11:27,360 --> 00:11:28,560
We have plenty of manpower.

220
00:11:28,560 --> 00:11:30,760
But doesn't mining take a lot of effort?

221
00:11:31,040 --> 00:11:33,320
Dig. If there isn't any,

222
00:11:34,200 --> 00:11:36,200
I have plenty of strength and means.

223
00:11:36,360 --> 00:11:37,200
What if there is?

224
00:11:37,200 --> 00:11:38,240
Absolutely impossible.

225
00:11:38,240 --> 00:11:40,160
I think you're just afraid we'll kill you,

226
00:11:40,160 --> 00:11:42,020
and are making up lies to trick us.

227
00:11:42,720 --> 00:11:45,040
He has a delicate face.

228
00:11:45,040 --> 00:11:48,760
If we sell him to a male brothel,

229
00:11:49,680 --> 00:11:50,880
the people there

230
00:11:50,880 --> 00:11:53,280
will love a pretty boy like him.

231
00:11:56,640 --> 00:11:57,200
Brother.

232
00:11:57,200 --> 00:11:59,000
Look at this one, strong and sturdy.

233
00:11:59,000 --> 00:12:00,930
Let's keep him to do the hard labor.

234
00:12:04,520 --> 00:12:05,600
Well.

235
00:12:07,040 --> 00:12:09,700
Leave this scholar for Doukou to be her husband.

236
00:12:09,880 --> 00:12:12,640
He's the only one who looks like a good guy here.

237
00:12:13,680 --> 00:12:14,760
Hey, brother.

238
00:12:14,960 --> 00:12:16,490
What are you talking about?

239
00:12:17,520 --> 00:12:18,880
Hey, sister.

240
00:12:19,560 --> 00:12:20,960
Brother.

241
00:12:20,960 --> 00:12:23,820
She's been shy since she was little. Don't you know?

242
00:12:24,120 --> 00:12:26,560
Look at her. She's quite pretty.

243
00:12:26,720 --> 00:12:28,120
What if we

244
00:12:28,120 --> 00:12:30,920
sell her to the Hongxiu Brothel?

245
00:12:31,800 --> 00:12:33,860
We can definitely make a lot of money.

246
00:12:33,920 --> 00:12:34,960
If he does,

247
00:12:36,400 --> 00:12:37,200
whip him.

248
00:12:37,920 --> 00:12:39,000
You want to whip me?

249
00:12:39,240 --> 00:12:40,480
I'll lay it on the line today.

250
00:12:40,480 --> 00:12:41,560
If you can dig up a gold mine,

251
00:12:41,560 --> 00:12:44,220
I'll twist my head off for you to kick like a ball.

252
00:13:53,600 --> 00:13:54,640
Right here.

253
00:13:58,680 --> 00:14:00,680
Are you kidding us in the middle of the night?

254
00:14:00,680 --> 00:14:02,810
You aren't trying to run away, are you?

255
00:14:03,760 --> 00:14:05,200
The Second Boss has extraordinary skills.

256
00:14:05,200 --> 00:14:06,040
Where could I run?

257
00:14:06,040 --> 00:14:07,300
What are you afraid of?

258
00:14:08,120 --> 00:14:09,160
Glad you know your place.

259
00:14:09,160 --> 00:14:10,080
I'll untie you.

260
00:14:13,200 --> 00:14:15,660
You're playing dumb to take advantage of us.

261
00:15:24,120 --> 00:15:25,840
Are you crazy?

262
00:15:37,960 --> 00:15:39,490
It turned white instantly.

263
00:15:42,480 --> 00:15:44,400
I've seen hair turn white overnight,

264
00:15:44,400 --> 00:15:46,440
but never instantly like this.

265
00:15:49,520 --> 00:15:52,120
He threw up blood just from touching the stone.

266
00:15:52,200 --> 00:15:54,860
Could he be terminally ill and trying to scam us?

267
00:15:56,880 --> 00:15:58,280
The gold mine is right here.

268
00:15:58,280 --> 00:15:59,240
Start digging.

269
00:15:59,240 --> 00:16:00,000
Boy.

270
00:16:00,480 --> 00:16:02,480
Digging a mountain is no small task.

271
00:16:02,520 --> 00:16:03,640
If you dare lie to me,

272
00:16:03,640 --> 00:16:05,320
you'll walk into this stronghold

273
00:16:05,320 --> 00:16:06,560
and be carried out dead.

274
00:16:06,560 --> 00:16:07,820
Quick, go get someone.

275
00:16:08,040 --> 00:16:08,560
Yes.

276
00:16:20,280 --> 00:16:21,480
Let me.

277
00:16:22,720 --> 00:16:24,040
Alright, you do it.

278
00:16:34,480 --> 00:16:36,800
You're really strong, little sister.

279
00:16:37,680 --> 00:16:38,960
Your stronghold

280
00:16:38,960 --> 00:16:40,420
really is full of talents.

281
00:16:45,920 --> 00:16:47,080
Oh, Boss.

282
00:16:47,080 --> 00:16:49,360
Boss, look, there really is gold.

283
00:16:49,360 --> 00:16:51,240
This is real gold, look.

284
00:16:53,320 --> 00:16:54,780
Gold-finding technique.

285
00:16:54,800 --> 00:16:56,400
You're from the Helian clan.

286
00:16:58,800 --> 00:17:01,240
I hope you two chiefs can keep this a secret for me.

